backup your current setup of add-start, simply copy /usr/local/bin/add-start to a safe location.
copy ./add-start to /usr/local/bin/add-start
give it execute permissions
chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/add-start

copy desktop_tool.py to /usr/local/bin/desktop_tool.py as root
    cp ./desktop_tool.py /usr/local/bin/desktop_tool.py
and give it execute permisions
    chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/desktop_tool.py
    
run add-start as you normally do to enjoy.
